fixedListComponent.text:
I am writing this recommendation to support Jamie Schultz. I have had the pleasure of working with Jamie as a coworker, direct report, and in his previous roles as Chief Technical Officer and Strategic Partner.

I worked directly for Jamie when he was the Director of IT at Medford Medical Clinic. As the director, Jamie initiated and led several infrastructure improvements including deploying virtual servers, wireless infrastructure, and Microsoft and Apple Software servers. Jamie also initiated and led meetings with with his peers at other companies to share ideas and strategies to improve services to stakeholders. Jamie cares about his employees and worked tirelessly to make sure we had the training and resources to accomplish our mission.

As a strategic partner, Jamie is excellent at working to build teams to resolve issues that arise. Hospital executives know that they can bring issues to him and he will build the team and gather resources necessary to resolve their issues quickly. Jamie cares deeply about making sure that our IT systems work and that any problems are quickly resolved. Jamie and I often picked each other's brains for ideas and solutions while he was the Chief Technology Officer at Providence University.

Jamie will be a great asset for the company fortunate enough to hire him. Wherever he lands, I would be the first in line to apply to work on his team if we still worked in the same area. I know that he will work to make his organization the best that it can be and those fortunate enough to work for him will be challenged to be their best.
